parameters:
You knew everything about the situation when we
first met, right?

I've become able to use clairvoyance magic a
little, but it tires me out.

I'm not watching all the time. Besides, Masamune
starts rustling around in bed from this time.
I didn't look because I wanted to!
And she's murmuring Amelia's name too.
I managed to avoid the second time, didn't I!
Don't you go showing off either.

Ah, I got it, I got it. If you're done with your
business, hurry up and go back.

Ah... I didn't come here to tell you not to watch
me masturbate.

I've become stronger since last time. It might be
due to the influence of retaining memories from
battle experience, but it's not just that.

The power and accuracy of magic have purely
increased.

Ah, I didn't explain it in detail. I thought you
didn't need to know.
It's not something worth hiding, so I'll tell you.

My magic to turn back time can rewind all events
as if they never happened.

However, there are things that cannot be undone.
Things that are affected by me and my magical
power.
What do you mean by the influence of magic power?

For example, the contractee. I have bestowed upon
Masamune a portion of my magical power.

So that's why Masamune is able to escape from the
rewind.
Using the power of demons... without permission?

There are no demons or humans in magical power.
You should be grateful that it has made you
stronger.

Was it thanks to Leviathan's magical power that I
suddenly became stronger?

Although it's just a little bit. It's not enough
to make a big difference.

It's probably because the experience points I
trained in the previous loop are still alive.

You should continue to train. The enemies will
likely be stronger than Masamune.

(I'm glad to become stronger, but I never expected
to gain demonic power...)

Let's do our best today. We should also attend
classes properly as students.
